item.coloph: brjod med kyi bshags pa rdzogs so

item.tib: dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad gyi bshags pa
slob dpon po sti ram tis mdzad pa
item.coloph: slob dpon po sti ram tis mdzad pa rdzogs so

item.tib: 'phags pa gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje gos sngon can gyi bshags pa
lus ngag yid gsum gyi bshags pa
phyag dor gyi bshags pa
khro bo yab yum gyi bshags pa
lha ru tra thar pa nag po'i smre bshags
rdo rje gzhon nu'i bshags pa
'jam dpal gyi bshags pa
zhi 'brel
sku gsung gi bshags pa
lhag tshog gi bshags pa
dug lnga'i bshags pa
rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen mo
item.skttrans: ma hA ma yu ri b+hidya ra d+nyi

item.coloph: gsang sngags chen po rjes su 'dzin pa'i mdo rdzogs so//

dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dgongs pa lung bstan pa/_/zhes bya ba rnal 'byor/_/chen po'i rgyud rdzogs s+hyo// //rgya gar gyi mkhan po d+harma shri pad+tra dang/_zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos zhus te gtan la phab po//

zhes bya ba rdzogs so// //rdo rje gsum gyi rnal 'byor grub pa'i dam la phyag 'tshal lo//_thugs dam rtsa ba'i snying po//_thig dpal dpe med lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag khang du//_rgya gar gyi mkhan po su dzA na shrI dz+nyA na dang//_sgra bsgyur gyi lo ts+tsha ba chen po bod kyi lha btsan po//_ bla ma dge slong zhi ba'i 'od kyi zhal snga nas//_bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o // //rgyud rgyal gsang 'dus bde mchog la sogs pa//_thams cad shes rab spyin yid gongs pa 'grel//_bshad rgyud rdo rje 'phreng bzhes rje rgyal gtsug po'i drin gyis bde bar bskyur//_bshad pa'i gdams pa bla ma'i gtan la phab//_nyi ma'i 'od bzhin kun x snang bar shog/ slad kyis kyang paN+Di ta kha chen rad badzra dang//_bla ma gnyen nam pas bcos shing bzhus te gtan la phab gnas//_rgyud pa'i gdam ngag dang bcas pa byas so//_bde legs su byar gcig//_dge'o//_shub+haM//
